{"tid":1159662,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"D10早場開心踢","createTime":"2019-05-18T01:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T11:05:26.000Z","uid":236969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fb59ffdfceede0e9e373a174c5b2515f5f6c49cb","tid":1159662,"uid":236969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"我和朋友喜歡踢雙前入攝。 <br />\n<br />\n有無朋友有興趣踢早場7-11St？（需兼任any，三個人輪流踢any無咁辛苦。）放心，只輕鬆踢D10。 <br />\n<br />\n有固定中路傳球路線和入攝方法。 <br />\n<br />\n有意請加Monster_Tazbb<br />\n<br />\n誠求打慣柱躉前鋒的玩家。"},{"pid":"b4d9a323a47e262640387f89e065ae0ea185354c","tid":1159662,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"藍田伊巴入得？"},{"pid":"be3d6558cbdf3e52dfa26cf43cac42c82a0a9ffd","tid":1159662,"uid":236969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"跪求藍田伊巴，我今日三點開始踢啊，跪求想試打雙前入攝的朋友加我Psn好友"},{"pid":"6969e9be999658621143b6c104c4edc465764a41","tid":1159662,"uid":236969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T10:12:46.000Z","msg":"已齊人，謝"},{"pid":"44c175267ec0df4924755b64a5fd489879e8e93f","tid":1159662,"uid":236969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"貪心點，基本已齊人，但想看看找不找到更多人踢七到十一早場，我們晚晚有波開，踢41212 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想找一隻右或左中場（不是翼鋒，負責在中場幫忙短傳），一隻cdm。最好能夠兼任any。大家輪流控any不會太累。"},{"pid":"c161b1996406e18ea2eb7d727db0724294701bd0","tid":1159662,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44c175267ec0df4924755b64a5fd489879e8e93f","tid":1159662,"uid":236969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"貪心點，基本已齊人，但想看看找不找到更多人踢七到十一早場，我們晚晚有波開，踢41212 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想找一隻右或左中場（不是翼鋒，負責在中場幫忙短傳），一隻cdm。最好能夠兼任any。大家輪流控any不會太累。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"大約踢幾點？ 打開cdm cm cam"},{"pid":"2e1476017252f31f20fcd21b83f9098dc0c52c0e","tid":1159662,"uid":236969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim